reviewText: This is an Anointed women of God. She has a voice and a range like no other. I had the pleasure of hearing her live, and it was dynamic! She definantly has "it".!

This video is absolutely awesome.  You get to experience a couple of her sisters and mom sing, and Karen Clark-Sheard, amongst others.  She is backed by an anointed choir and musicians.  Amazon.com please continue to make videos by Lashaun Pace available to your customers.  I have been truly blessed!!
